  ('I', 10, $wiki_seed_v1$Intuitive Solving 直观还原$wiki_seed_v1$, $wiki_seed_v1$Intuitive solving consists in solving the Rubik's cube without using any algorithm that you do not understand. In most methods, for example for the last layer, most algorithm are used in such way that there is an input cube in some state, then you apply the appropriate algorithm that you learnt by heart, and quite magically, the cube is in the desired state.$wiki_seed_v1$, 'seed'),
  ('I', 11, $wiki_seed_v1$Inverse 逆序, 逆预设$wiki_seed_v1$, $wiki_seed_v1$The inverse of A B C is C' B' A'. A B C的逆序是C' B' A'.$wiki_seed_v1$, 'seed'),
